originalText.text: I loved the experience of my elopement with One Wedding House. They were great from beginning to end and made the process very easy and stress free. The photos came out absolutely fabulous and couldn’t be happier of the moments captured. I highly recommend you consider them for your elopement or wedding it was worth it.

originalText.text:
We had the most amazing wedding experience with One Wedding House! Their all-in-one package made the planning process seamless and stress-free. From start to finish, they took care of every detail, ensuring that our special day was absolutely perfect.

The team at One Wedding House went above and beyond to bring our vision to life. They listened to our ideas and provided expert guidance along the way. The level of professionalism and attention to detail was exceptional.

The photography and videography captured every precious moment, allowing us to relive our wedding day over and over again. The talented team ensured that no moment was missed, and the results were breathtaking.

What sets One Wedding House apart is their genuine care for their clients. They treated us like family and made us feel truly special throughout the entire process. Their passion for creating unforgettable memories was evident in every interaction.

We cannot recommend One Wedding House enough.

originalText.text: Working with One Wedding House was an absolute DELIGHT! The packages they offer really have everything you need. They are professional, super timely and so accommodating. They were flexible about our wedding being closer to a micro-wedding with about 50 people in NJ. And they are so talented! From Yekaterina's planning, coordinating and officiating, to Lana and Danil's video/photography, to their HMU person, to the florist and the musician. Everyone who is part of their crew is absolutely amazing at what they do. My husband and I will be forever grateful for finding and working with them for our most special day.
